RT @vrumbleapp: Did you know that you will be able to relax between #NFT battles in the Vrumble #AR Island world? Collect some supplies, in‚Ä¶

As our journeys are recorded, the Sporos community will be creating the story of the Sporos as a "creative collective." A single story, written by the community, that evolves along with your Sporo over time.

Join the Sporos community, and let's create a new world together!

The next step will be the interface for playing through the stories. The first story will be the prolog to the story and will set the stage for future stories. The interactive stories will allow you to record your journey to continue to build your Sporos own story.

The team is currently working on a few tools to enable this experience. The first of which will be the Sporo character editor. This will allow you to name your Sporo, create their back story, and further customize your character. We expect to have the early version released soon.

@husker3eleven Your journey will unfold in a series of "Missions" you will play as your Sporo. The team plans to use fables, legends, and other folk lore from many cultures both current and past. In addition to these we are building our own storyverse with its own lore.

The Sporos project is a character building NFT project that takes holders on an interactive journey of self-discovery and self-expression.
